<a name="torch_of_alna"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Torch of Alna</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">1H Blunt</a><BR>
Damage per second - 5.20<BR>
Damage 6 - Delay 25<BR>
Weight: 3.5 - DEF, ERU, GNM, HIE, HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/magician/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">MAG</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/reclaim_energy.shtml?spellID=346">Reclaim Energy</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(INT +2) (Sv Fire +5) </font>
<BR>
Submitted By: TregareUS<BR>

