<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>the Shovel, the Stein, the Torch and the Broom are the magicians focus items. It allow the to make more powerful pets. The shovel is for earth pets. The stein is for water pets. The torch is for fire pets. The broom is for air pets.<BR>
